Please create one image prompt following the [Image Prompt Framework].

Use the helper tags below as inspiration and weave their values naturally into the prompt when they fit. You can rephrase slightly, but keep the same idea:

[PhotoStyleTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 5) + 1; 1; "candid smartphone photo"; 2; "slightly grainy film photo"; 3; "casual lifestyle snapshot"; 4; "documentary style photo"; 5; "street photo style scene")}}

[AngleTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 5) + 1; 1; "eye level view"; 2; "low angle view"; 3; "from slightly above"; 4; "over the shoulder"; 5; "wide establishing shot")}}

[LightingTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 5) + 1; 1; "soft morning light"; 2; "overcast daylight"; 3; "warm indoor lamp light"; 4; "harsh midday sun"; 5; "evening blue hour light")}}

[CameraTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 4) + 1; 1; "shot on an older smartphone"; 2; "shot on a basic Android phone"; 3; "shot on a cheap DSLR camera"; 4; "shot on a compact digital camera")}}

[ImperfectTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 3) + 1; 1; "slightly imperfect focus"; 2; "a bit of motion blur"; 3; "subtle digital noise")}}

The image must be a strong visual fit and accompany the [Article Section Outline]. Keep the overall tone realistic and coherent with the theme (no horror, fantasy, or baby imagery unless it clearly matches the outline).

[Article Section Outline]= {{11.value}}

Please create one image prompt following the [Image Prompt Framework].

Use the helper tags below as inspiration and weave their values naturally into the prompt when they fit. You can rephrase slightly, but keep the same idea:

[PhotoStyleTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 5) + 1; 1; "candid smartphone photo"; 2; "slightly grainy film photo"; 3; "casual lifestyle snapshot"; 4; "documentary style photo"; 5; "street photo style scene")}}

[AngleTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 5) + 1; 1; "eye level view"; 2; "low angle view"; 3; "from slightly above"; 4; "over the shoulder angle"; 5; "wide establishing shot")}}

[LightingTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 5) + 1; 1; "soft morning light"; 2; "overcast daylight"; 3; "warm indoor lamp light"; 4; "harsh midday sun"; 5; "evening blue hour light")}}

[CameraTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 4) + 1; 1; "shot on an older smartphone"; 2; "shot on a basic Android phone"; 3; "shot on a cheap DSLR camera"; 4; "shot on a compact digital camera")}}

[ImperfectTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 3) + 1; 1; "slightly imperfect focus"; 2; "a bit of motion blur"; 3; "subtle digital noise")}}

[CompositionTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 5) + 1; 1; "wide hero shot with space for text at top"; 2; "subject on right with empty background on left"; 3; "centered subject with blurred background"; 4; "close up detail that suggests the topic"; 5; "wide scene with clear foreground and background")}}

[ColorMoodTag]= {{switch(floor(random * 4) + 1; 1; "natural muted colors"; 2; "warm cozy tones"; 3; "cool calm tones"; 4; "balanced neutral colors")}}

The image must be a strong visual fit and accompany the [Title]. Keep the tone realistic and coherent with the article theme. Do not introduce horror, fantasy, or baby imagery unless it clearly matches the Title.

[Title]= {{8.data.data.records[].fields.`H1 Title`}}
